  METHOD zif_myfi_document~out_header.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_CONTRACT~zif_myfi_document~out_header
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 21/09/20 290977SCN RD2K919977 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002096: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.2)
* 30.11.20 220977FKC RD2K920449 DS-11-32-07-01 6000002172: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3)
*                                              Enable legacy i.e. non-myfi created docs
* 04.08.21 210983DY RD2K921440  DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002451: MyFi Purchasing (August Release)
*                                              Enable Your reference field in MyFi Purchasing
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
    DATA: lv_amount TYPE /bcv/sin_dec16_3.
    me->map_bapi_2_odata(
      EXPORTING
        is_sending_structure = gs_oaheader
      IMPORTING
        es_data              = gs_contract_deep ).

    gs_contract_deep-ihrez = gs_oaheader-ref_1.
    SELECT SINGLE name1 FROM lfa1 INTO gs_contract_deep-vendorname WHERE lifnr = gs_contract_deep-vendor.
    CASE me->gv_doc_type.
      WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_myfi_doc_type-l4l_oa.
        gs_contract_deep-issinglepo = abap_true.
      WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_myfi_doc_type-myfi_oa.
        gs_contract_deep-iscontractonly = abap_true.
      WHEN OTHERS.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_amount  = zcl_mfp_utilities=>convert_curr_format(
      iv_amount = gs_oaheader-acum_value
      iv_curr   = gs_oaheader-currency ).

    gs_contract_deep-acum_value = lv_amount.
    IF me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-status IS INITIAL.
      me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-status = zcl_mfp_utilities=>translate_mm_status_to_mfp( gs_oaheader-po_rel_ind ).
    ENDIF.
    gs_contract_deep-status = me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-status.
    gs_contract_deep-statusdesclong = gs_contract_deep-statusdesc = zcl_mfp_utilities=>get_status_desc( me->zif_myfi_document~old_doc_header-status ).

  ENDMETHOD.


  METHOD zif_myfi_document~out_line_items.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_CONTRACT~zif_myfi_document~out_line_items
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 21/09/20 290977SCN RD2K919977 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002096: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.2)
* 21.10.20 290977SCN RD2K919656 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002172: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3) Changed - UOM Changeable Flag
* 30/11/20 210983DY  RD2K919656 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002172: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3)
*                                             Additional logic for Texts and free item
* 14/01/21 210983DY  RD2K920558 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002251: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3 Defect Fixes)
*                               Additional code to fix Line Item Texts  with line break
* 03/03/21 210983DY  RD2K920554 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002250: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.4 )
*                               Additional code to handle Multi Currency Outline Agreements
* 16.04.21 210983DY RD2K920923  DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002348: MyFi Purchasing (May Release)
*                               Additional logic to handle currencey translation ratio for
*                               Multiple Currenecies
* 20/05/21 210983DY  RD2K921041 DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002393: June DFSS release for MyFi Purchasing
*                               Additional code to check and derive exchange rate for line items
* 05/11/21 210983DY  RD2K922034 DS-11-32-07-01 S6000002550: MyFi Applications (December Release)
*                    Additional code to enable Multi Account Assignment
* 21.06.2022 210983DY RD2K922841 MyFi Continuous Improvement July Release
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*CALL METHOD SUPER->ZIF_MYFI_DOCUMENT~OUT_LINE_ITEMS
*    .
    DATA: ls_lineitem        TYPE bapimeoutitem,
          ls_odata_lineitem  TYPE zcl_zedm_mfp_mpc=>ts_lineitem,
          lt_odata_lineitems TYPE TABLE OF zcl_zedm_mfp_mpc=>ts_lineitem WITH DEFAULT KEY,
          lt_ekkn            TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ekkn,
          lv_item            TYPE ebelp,
          lv_budget_exchrate TYPE kursf_char,
          lv_exchange        TYPE wkurs,
          ls_ekkn            TYPE ekkn,
          lv_amount_doc      TYPE bapicurr_d, " bwert,
          lv_netprice        TYPE bapicurext,
          ls_item_extension  TYPE bapi_te_meoutitem,
*          lt_ekab            TYPE TABLE OF ekab,
          lt_ebeln           TYPE mmpur_t_ebeln,
          ls_ebeln           TYPE mmpur_s_ebeln.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS :
                    <ls_item_condition>   TYPE          bapimeoutcondition.

    CLEAR : lv_budget_exchrate.

* 2.4 Determine if it is multi currency agreement or Foreign Currency Outline agreement

    DATA(l_multi_curr_oa) = zcl_mfp_utilities=>multi_currency_oa(
                i_ebeln = me->gs_contract_deep-contractnumber
                i_waers = me->gs_contract_deep-currency ).

    IF l_multi_curr_oa = abap_true.
      me->gv_multi_currency = abap_true.

    ELSEIF me->gs_contract_deep-currency NE 'AUD'.
      DATA(lv_doc_foreigncurrency) = abap_true.
    ENDIF.
* Get Purchase Order's associated with Contract
    SELECT konnr, ktpnr, ebeln, ebelp, menge, netwr, waers, wkurs
       FROM ekab INTO TABLE @DATA(lt_ekab)
       WHERE konnr EQ @me->gs_contract_deep-contractnumber
                            ORDER BY ebeln ASCENDING.
* Read the EKKN account assignment data to get the ESP field as the BAPI ExtensionOut can't be used for this
* as the OA line item and sequence (ZEKKN) are missing from the BAPI Extension output
    SELECT *
      FROM ekkn
      INTO TABLE lt_ekkn
     WHERE ebeln = me->gs_contract_deep-contractnumber
       AND zekkn = '01'.  " Only get the first account assignment row as the app only handles one Acct Assignment

    LOOP AT gt_oaitems INTO ls_lineitem.

      me->map_bapi_2_odata(
        EXPORTING
          is_sending_structure   = ls_lineitem
        IMPORTING
          es_data                = ls_odata_lineitem
      ).

      ls_odata_lineitem-distrib = ls_lineitem-distrib.
      ls_odata_lineitem-part_inv = ls_lineitem-part_inv.
      IF NOT ls_lineitem-trackingno IS INITIAL.
        ls_odata_lineitem-trackingno = ls_lineitem-trackingno.
      ENDIF.

      IF NOT ls_lineitem-vend_mat IS INITIAL.
        ls_odata_lineitem-vendormaterial = ls_lineitem-vend_mat.
      ENDIF.

* Set zero value indicator
      IF ls_lineitem-net_price = '0.00'
      AND ls_lineitem-gr_ind = abap_false
      AND ls_lineitem-ir_ind = abap_false
      AND ls_lineitem-gr_basediv = abap_false .
        ls_odata_lineitem-zerovalue = abap_true.
      ENDIF.

      lv_item = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber.
* Get line item texts
      ls_odata_lineitem-itemtext = convert_mm_table_str_item( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oaitemtext iv_item = lv_item
                                                                                           iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-item-text ).

      ls_odata_lineitem-inforecordpotext = convert_mm_table_str_item( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oaitemtext iv_item = lv_item
                                                                                   iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-item-info_record ).

      ls_odata_lineitem-materialpotext =   convert_mm_table_str_item( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oaitemtext iv_item = lv_item
                                                                                        iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-item-mat_po ).

      ls_odata_lineitem-inforecordnote = convert_mm_table_str_item( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oaitemtext iv_item = lv_item
                                                                                        iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-item-info_note ).

*Commented for december releaase
***      READ TABLE gt_oaaccounts WITH KEY item_no = ls_lineitem-item_no INTO DATA(ls_account).
***      IF sy-subrc IS INITIAL.
***        me->map_bapi_2_odata(
***          EXPORTING
***            is_sending_structure   = ls_account
***          IMPORTING
***            es_data                = ls_odata_lineitem
***        ).
***      ENDIF.
      IF ls_odata_lineitem-distrib IS INITIAL.
        ls_odata_lineitem-distrib = '0'.
      ENDIF.
* ESP
      READ TABLE lt_ekkn INTO ls_ekkn
        WITH KEY ebelp = ls_lineitem-item_no.

      IF sy-subrc = 0.
        ls_odata_lineitem-esp = ls_ekkn-zzesp.
      ENDIF.

      get_quantity_left( CHANGING is_odata_lineitem = ls_odata_lineitem ).

      ls_odata_lineitem-parentnumber = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber.
* Fetch line item currrency for outline agreements from condition record
      LOOP AT gt_oacond_valid_item INTO DATA(ls_oacond_valid_item)  WHERE valid_from LE sy-datum AND
                                         valid_to   GE sy-datum AND
                                         item_no = ls_lineitem-item_no.
        READ TABLE gt_oacondition_item ASSIGNING <ls_item_condition>  WITH KEY item_no = ls_lineitem-item_no
        serial_id = ls_oacond_valid_item-serial_id
        cond_type = 'PB00'.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit = <ls_item_condition>-cond_value.
          ls_odata_lineitem-net_price = <ls_item_condition>-cond_value.
          ls_lineitem-net_price = <ls_item_condition>-cond_value.
          ls_odata_lineitem-currency = <ls_item_condition>-currency.
        ELSE.
          ls_odata_lineitem-currency = gs_contract_deep-currency.
        ENDIF.
      ENDLOOP.

*      For expired condition record, get currency from header
      IF ls_odata_lineitem-currency IS INITIAL.
        ls_odata_lineitem-currency = gs_contract_deep-currency.
      ENDIF.
      DATA(lv_factor) = zcl_mfp_utilities=>get_currency_factor(
               iv_currency = ls_odata_lineitem-currency ).
* In case of multi currency OA, clculate net price in document currency and unassigned value
      IF l_multi_curr_oa = abap_true.

* Get all PO's associated to a OA Line Item
        LOOP AT lt_ekab INTO DATA(ls_ekab) WHERE konnr = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber AND
                                                        ktpnr = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber.

          ls_ebeln = 'IEQ'. ls_ebeln-low = ls_ekab-ebeln.
          APPEND ls_ebeln TO lt_ebeln. CLEAR ls_ebeln.
        ENDLOOP.

* Exchange rate maintained on OA Line Item in UI is stored in EKPO as appended structure Field
* which is derived from BAPI in one of the extension structure's
        READ TABLE gt_extensionout WITH KEY valuepart1(5) = ls_lineitem-item_no
                                            structure = 'BAPI_TE_MEOUTITEM' INTO DATA(ls_ext).

        MOVE ls_ext-valuepart1 TO ls_item_extension.

        IF NOT ls_odata_lineitem-currency = gs_contract_deep-currency.
          IF NOT ls_item_extension-kursf IS INITIAL.
* For OA's created in UI, exchange rate is derived from extension structure
            lv_budget_exchrate = ls_item_extension-kursf.
          ELSE.

* For legacy OA's derive exchange rate from PO's associated with OA line item
            lv_budget_exchrate = zcl_mfp_utilities=>get_budget_exchangerate( it_ebeln = lt_ebeln ).
          ENDIF.
        ENDIF.

        IF lv_budget_exchrate IS INITIAL.
          lv_budget_exchrate = gs_contract_deep-exch_rate.
        ENDIF.
        CLEAR : lt_ebeln.

* For OA Line item which has PO's associated to it
        IF line_exists( lt_ekab[ konnr = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber
                                 ktpnr = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber  ] ).

          LOOP AT lt_ekab INTO ls_ekab WHERE konnr = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber AND
                                                ktpnr = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber.

            DATA: lv_netvalue TYPE bapicurr_d.
            lv_netvalue = ls_ekab-netwr.

            DATA(lv_netwr) = zcl_mfp_document=>convert_currency_decimal( iv_waers = ls_ekab-waers iv_netwr = lv_netvalue ).

            ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr + lv_netwr * ls_ekab-wkurs.

            ls_odata_lineitem-qtyassigned = ls_odata_lineitem-qtyassigned + ls_ekab-menge.
          ENDLOOP.

* For OA Line item with no PO's associated yet
        ELSE.
*  Net Price in Document currency is calculated as Unit Price * Target Quantity * Exchange rate
          ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit * ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty * lv_budget_exchrate.

        ENDIF.

* Calculate Value assigned in Document Currency, UI will use this value for validations
        " OA Item partly assigned to PO
        IF NOT ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft IS INITIAL AND
           NOT ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft EQ ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.

          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr.
          lv_exchange = lv_budget_exchrate.
          lv_netprice = ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft * ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit * lv_exchange. " Budget exchange rate should be used here for unassigned value
          ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr + lv_netprice.

          " No PO created
        ELSEIF ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft EQ ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.
          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = '0.00'.

          " OA line item is completely converted to PO item
        ELSE.
          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr.
        ENDIF.
        ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr / lv_factor.
        IF ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr NE '0.00'.
          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr / lv_factor.
        ENDIF.
        ls_odata_lineitem-exchrate_budget = lv_budget_exchrate.
        CLEAR lv_budget_exchrate.
*  In case of OA with non-AUD Document currency, calculate net price in document currency
      ELSEIF lv_doc_foreigncurrency = abap_true. " For document in foreign currency

* For OA Line item which has PO's associated to it
        IF line_exists( lt_ekab[ konnr = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber
                                 ktpnr = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber  ] ).

          LOOP AT lt_ekab INTO ls_ekab WHERE konnr = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber AND
                                                ktpnr = ls_odata_lineitem-linenumber.

            lv_netvalue = ls_ekab-netwr.

            lv_netwr = zcl_mfp_document=>convert_currency_decimal( iv_waers = ls_ekab-waers iv_netwr = lv_netvalue ).

            ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr + lv_netwr." * ls_ekab-wkurs.

            ls_odata_lineitem-qtyassigned = ls_odata_lineitem-qtyassigned + ls_ekab-menge.
          ENDLOOP.

* For OA Line item with no PO's associated yet
        ELSE.
*  Net Price in Document currency is calculated as Unit Price * Target Quantity * Exchange rate
          ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit * ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.

        ENDIF.

*No need to pass exchange rate to line item for foreign currency documents
**        ls_odata_lineitem-exchrate_budget  = gs_contract_deep-exch_rate.
**        lv_budget_exchrate = ls_odata_lineitem-exchrate_budget.
        IF NOT ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft IS INITIAL AND
           NOT ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft EQ ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.

          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr.
          lv_netprice = ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft * ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit.
          ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr + lv_netprice.

          " No PO created
        ELSEIF ls_odata_lineitem-qtyleft EQ ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.
          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = '0.00'.
          ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit * ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty. " Feb release


        ELSE.
          ls_odata_lineitem-valassigned_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr.
        ENDIF.
*        ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr / lv_factor.

      ELSE.
        ls_odata_lineitem-netprice_doccurr = ls_odata_lineitem-price_unit * ls_odata_lineitem-target_qty.
        ls_odata_lineitem-exchrate_budget  = gs_contract_deep-exch_rate.
      ENDIF.

* Current value to doc currency by adjusting decimals

      SELECT SINGLE mseh3 FROM  t006a
       WHERE  spras  = 'E'
       AND    msehi  = @ls_lineitem-orderpr_un
       INTO @ls_odata_lineitem-po_unit.

*Delete or Non Delete flag
      ls_odata_lineitem-non_delete = abap_false.
* UOM Changeable

*      SELECT SINGLE ebeln FROM ekab
*      INTO @DATA(lv_ebeln)
*      WHERE konnr EQ @me->gs_contract_deep-contractnumber AND
*            ktpnr EQ @ls_lineitem-item_no.
*      IF sy-subrc EQ 0.
*        ls_odata_lineitem-uom_changeable = abap_false.
*      ELSE.
      ls_odata_lineitem-uom_changeable = abap_true.
*      ENDIF.

      APPEND ls_odata_lineitem TO lt_odata_lineitems.
      CLEAR : ls_odata_lineitem.

    ENDLOOP.

    gs_contract_deep-contractlis = lt_odata_lineitems.

  ENDMETHOD.


  METHOD zif_myfi_document~out_strings.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_DOCUMENT_CONTRACT~zif_myfi_document~out_strings
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for MyFi Documents
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
* 30/11/20 210983DY  RD2K919656 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002172: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.3)
*                                      Additional logic for Texts and free item
* 03/03/21 210983DY  RD2K920554 DS-11-32-07-01 S 6000002250: MyFi Purchasing (Release 2.4 )
*                               Additional logic to handle Multi delivery address
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <string_record> LIKE LINE OF me->zif_myfi_document~old_strings.

    me->gs_contract_deep-romancomment = convert_mm_table_string( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oatextheader
                                                                           iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-header ).
* Header Note
    me->gs_contract_deep-headertexts-headernote = convert_mm_table_string( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oatextheader
                                                                               iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-note ).
*Contract Riders
    me->gs_contract_deep-headertexts-contractriders = convert_mm_table_string( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oatextheader
                                                                               iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-riders ).

*Alternate Terms and Conditions

    DATA(lv_alternatetc) = convert_mm_table_string( EXPORTING it_texts  = gt_oatextheader
                                                                               iv_tdid   = zif_mfp_constants=>gc_header_text-oa-alt_tc_cond ).
    IF NOT lv_alternatetc IS INITIAL.
      me->gs_contract_deep-headertexts-alternatetc = abap_true.
    ELSE.
      me->gs_contract_deep-headertexts-alternatetc = abap_false.
    ENDIF.

    me->gs_contract_deep-headertexts-parentnumber = gs_contract_deep-contractnumber.


* Retrieve the strings table data from the me->zif_myfi_document~old_strings variable.
    LOOP AT me->zif_myfi_document~old_strings ASSIGNING <string_record>.

      CASE <string_record>-string_type.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-value_for_money.
          me->gs_contract_deep-approvaldetails-valueformoney = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-comment_approver.
          me->gs_contract_deep-approvaldetails-commentforapprover = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-reject_comment.
          me->gs_contract_deep-approvaldetails-rejectcomments = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-etp_justif.
          me->gs_contract_deep-admindetails-etp_justification = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-pickup_loc.
*          me->gs_contract_deep-contactdetails-pickuplocation = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-spec_instr.
          me->gs_contract_deep-contactdetails-specialinstructions = <string_record>-string_data.
        WHEN zif_mfp_constants=>gc_string_type-indig_no_appr.
          me->gs_contract_deep-admindetails-indig_no_approach_rsn = <string_record>-string_data.
      ENDCASE.

    ENDLOOP.

  ENDMETHOD.


  METHOD zif_myfi_document~reassign_doc.
